org.ensembl.datamodel
Interface AffyProbe

All Superinterfaces:
Persistent, java.io.Serializable
public interface AffyProbe
extends Persistent

An oligo spot from one or more Affymetric micro arrays. AffyProbes are grouped into probe sets and the same probe in the same set can appear in multiple arrays.

Author:
Craig Melsopp
